Mrs Sheetal.

359
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:16,760
And he is Mr Hemraj's son,
Mr Naren from Rajkot.

360
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:18,440
So, I have introduced you to all.

361
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:24,080
Vishakha, get the drinks.

362
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,280
Vishakha.

363
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:28,360
- I hope there was no problem
in coming here. - No problem.

364
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,680
Vishakha is here.

365
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,600
She is Vishakha,

366
00:21:34,320 --> 00:21:35,920
