00:22:42,560 --> 00:22:46,120
If you want to talk to Vishakha,

382
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:48,920
- you can talk to her.
- Actually...

383
00:22:49,080 --> 00:22:51,640
Vishakha, take him
to the garden outside.

